<HEADLINE>
<P>
MAN PLANNING TO TESTIFY IN EL SALVADOR DEATH SQUAD PROBE ARRESTED BY INS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A member of an El Salvador military intelligence unit linked to the murders of 
Jesuit priests in that country was arrested in Long Beach on Tuesday in the 
midst of a visit during which he planned to testify about the killings, 
activists said. 
</P>
<P>
