city, was arrested by Immigration and Naturalization Service agents on federal 
charges of illegally entering the United States after being deported on the 
same charge seven years ago. 
</P>
<P>
Activists seeking an end to U.S. involvement in El Salvador were trying to set 
up interviews between Joya-Martinez and a congressional committee investigating 
alleged death squad activity in the Central American country. 
</P>
