Photo, Horse-drawn hearse carrying body of homeless advocate Mitch Snyder leads 
a procession of Snyder's friends and supporters and Washington, D.C.-area 
homeless people down Pennsylvania Avenue. AL STEPHENSON / For The Times; Photo, 
