was as much political rally as funeral service. Actor Martin Sheen -- at the 
podium, above -- called him an "uncompromising and compassionate voice for 
social justice," while the Rev. Jesse Jackson -- at Sheen's side -- insisted 
the best eulogy would be to continue his work. Snyder was found dead last week, 
