<HEADLINE>
<P>
65 REPORTED SLAIN AT SOMALI SOCCER GAME 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
NAIROBI, Kenya 
</P>
