<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY NEWSMAKERS: EVERSOLE APPOINTED SENIOR VP AT TOSHIBA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Dennis E. Eversole has been named senior vice president, finance and 
administration, for Toshiba America Information Systems Inc. He succeeds 
Nobuteru Baba, who returned to Toshiba Corp., the Japanese parent company. 
Eversole had previously been vice president, finance, and corporate controller 
for the Irvine-based manufacturer of office products and telecommunication 
systems. Before joining Toshiba America in 1984, he was corporate controller 
for Citicorp/financial services. 
</P>
</TEXT>
